sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as Llama Stack Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Inline as Inline Provider<br/>(in-process)
    participant Remote as Remote Provider<br/>(in-process)
    participant Garak as Garak Subprocess<br/>(local CLI)
    participant KFP as KFP API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pipeline Pod
    participant vLLM as vLLM Model Endpoint<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Safety as Llama Stack Safety API<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Files as Llama Stack Files API<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3 / MinIO<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant SDG as SDG Model Endpoint<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant EvalHub as Eval-Hub Job<br/>(K8s Job)
    participant Adapter as GarakAdapter<br/>(in-process)

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,Files: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation (Llama Stack Provider)
        Client->>LLS: POST /eval/run_benchmark<br/>Auth: None (cluster-internal)
        LLS->>Inline: invoke GarakInlineEvalAdapter
        Inline->>Garak: spawn subprocess<br/>os.setsid() process group
        Garak->>vLLM: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (VLLM_API_TOKEN)
        vLLM-->>Garak: Model response
        Garak-->>Inline: JSONL results + exit code
        Inline->>Safety: POST /safety/run_shield<br/>Input/output guardrail scan
        Safety-->>Inline: Shield scan results
        Inline->>Files: POST /files/upload<br/>Reports, configs, datasets
        Files-->>Inline: File references
        Inline-->>LLS: EvalResult with artifacts
        LLS-->>Client: JSON response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over Client,SDG: Flow 2: Remote KFP Evaluation (Llama Stack Provider)
        Client->>LLS: POST /eval/run_benchmark<br/>Auth: None (cluster-internal)
        LLS->>Remote: invoke GarakRemoteEvalAdapter
        Remote->>KFP: Submit pipeline<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / SA
        KFP->>KFPPod: Schedule 6-step pipeline
        KFPPod->>Files: Step 1 (validate): download config
        Files-->>KFPPod: Config artifacts
        KFPPod->>Files: Step 2 (taxonomy): download taxonomy
        Files-->>KFPPod: Taxonomy data
        KFPPod->>SDG: Step 3 (sdg_generate)<br/>Auth: API Key (__FROM_ENV__)
        SDG-->>KFPPod: Synthetic adversarial prompts
        KFPPod->>vLLM: Step 4-5 (garak_scan)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        vLLM-->>KFPPod: Model responses
        KFPPod->>Files: Step 6 (parse_results): upload reports
        Files-->>KFPPod: File references
        Remote-->>LLS: EvalResult (async polling)
        LLS-->>Client: JSON response
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over EvalHub,S3: Flow 3: Eval-Hub KFP Evaluation
        EvalHub->>Adapter: run_benchmark_job()
        Adapter->>KFP: Submit 6-step pipeline<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        KFP->>KFPPod: Schedule pipeline
        KFPPod->>S3: Step 1 (validate): download config<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
        S3-->>KFPPod: Config artifacts
        KFPPod->>vLLM: Step 4 (garak_scan)<br/>Auth: API Key
        vLLM-->>KFPPod: Model responses
        KFPPod->>S3: Step 5: upload artifacts<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
        S3-->>KFPPod: Upload confirmation
        Adapter->>S3: Download results<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
        S3-->>Adapter: Scan artifacts
        Adapter->>Adapter: Parse results,<br/>generate HTML report
        Note over Adapter: Forward to eval-hub sidecar<br/>+ OCI registry + MLflow
    end
